{"tid":991894,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS/AN] PES2019 Mobile討論帖 (82）- 1001記得開psot!","createTime":"2019-01-22T17:20:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T23:52:04.000Z","uid":62293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e85a56cd609d6b435cff391ed64ab287999e1e95","tid":991894,"uid":62293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T17:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZdwQZXy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZdwQZXy.png&h=2e1408c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n● 官網：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.konami.com/wepes/mobile/en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.konami.com%2Fwepes%2Fmobile%2Fen%2F&d=u8%2Bqoai3bpL%2Fx%2BgE41AThMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=60c40651\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.konami.com/wepes/mobile/en/</a><br />\n● Download Link<br />\nIOS: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/pes-2018-pro-evolution-soccer/id1117270703?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fpes-2018-pro-evolution-soccer%2Fid1117270703%3Fmt%3D8&d=u8%2Bqoai3bpL%2Fx%2BgE41AThMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=bae0d35f\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/pes-2018-pro-evolution-soccer/id1117270703?mt=8</a><br />\nAndroid: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.konami.pesam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Djp.konami.pesam&d=u8%2Bqoai3bpL%2Fx%2BgE41AThMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=f8c2c616\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.konami.pesam</a><br />\n<br />\n● 新手開波Q&amp;A?<br />\n<br />\n1. 洗唔洗刷首抽?<br />\n新手開波既時候會有好多抽，盡量雙金/一黑起手，抽中既球員可以睇下下面既推薦List，如果無亦可以問下各位巴打，當然唔滿意既可以繼續刷到自己想要既球員為止。<br />\n<br />\n2. 點樣儲錢?<br />\n一開始既時候你會好窮，所以盡量用白銅銀波儲GP，例如用白銅銀波打活動或者用123星球探抽球員放，但隊中有一兩隻金黑都負擔得起。<br />\n<br />\n3. 遊戲玩法<br />\n盡量有活動既時候都打到30000TP，因為5000tp有銀波券，30000先金波券，而當中亦會有突破導師幫你心愛既球員提升LV上限<br />\n<br />\n而PVP活動，新手技巧唔高既話可以考慮用2 3星隊，因為4星5星都多勁人，pvp重視技術同隊伍，唔係盲目擺曬啲人落去就得，<br />\n<br />\n有咩問題可以再post上嚟問，相信巴打們都可以幫到你。<br />\n<br />\n4. 點樣改Email或者密碼?<br />\n<a href=\"https://my.konami.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmy.konami.net%2F&d=u8%2Bqoai3bpL%2Fx%2BgE41AThMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=73602fa1\" target=\"_blank\">https://my.konami.net/</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 操控方法<br />\n操控類型有 Advanced 同 Classic 揀<br />\n推薦 Classic 佢類似手制咁樣同埋易上手啲<br />\n<br />\n● 球員資料<br />\nPES DATABASE <br />\n<a href=\"http://pesdb.net/pes2019/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpesdb.net%2Fpes2019%2F&d=u8%2Bqoai3bpL%2Fx%2BgE41AThMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=995f3b3f\" target=\"_blank\">http://pesdb.net/pes2019/</a><br />\n要注意由於可能有球員更新，所以DATABASE 入面既100%抽球員可能有誤。<br />\n<br />\n只需要直接search球員名，你就可以搵到該球員特性同數值。<br />\n而想搵一堆某類球員，可以憑Search Conditions自行set Filters 搵出黎。<br />\n<br />\n 新手入game 第一件事畫質轉60fps <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h38hp4m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh38hp4m.jpg&h=66c1328d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d73ba7c8b2903474cf46e2ca2f833a48daccf9a","tid":991894,"uid":62293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T17:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0478489e924255323cf3efe1cb74a3f61d93f04b","tid":991894,"uid":207974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T17:26:32.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1390f934d771b0a2bf641889fd76b576ce629a08","tid":991894,"uid":204373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T17:26:52.000Z","msg":"第三項幾時改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c41d8abd2ac5390383b8db42b3898bf7e4c9fc","tid":991894,"uid":101892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T17:29